{"per_page":10,"total":16,"current":14,"data":[{"title":" 二次请求的错误","date":"2018-06-11T03:05:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/121","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"php 中empty和isset的区别","date":"2018-06-08T01:31:00.000Z","excerpt":"<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> if($order_type==1)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            $whereCondition = (!empty($order_id))&amp;&amp;(!empty($goodsid))&amp;&amp;(!empty($order_type))&amp;&amp;(!empty($level));</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           $whereCondition = (!empty($order_id))&amp;&amp;(!empty($goodsid))&amp;&amp;(!empty($order_type));</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">if($whereCondition)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t....</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>今天反了一个很低级的错误，如上述代码所写，第一个if是确定判断条件，判断条件必须都<strong>不空</strong>才行，而其中的一个参数<code>order_type</code>是<code>0</code>，但是<code>empty（）</code>是可以判断参数0或NULL返回true。这样虽然参数已经传了0，但是<code>！empty（）</code>也会返回一个false，这样不管怎么样 <code>if($whereCondition)</code>都会是<strong>false</strong>。这时应该用<code>isset（）</code>。</p>","link":"post/119","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"jQuery post提交数据","date":"2018-06-05T03:01:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>###html部分<br></p>","link":"post/117","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"sql DISTINCT 命令简单使用","date":"2018-06-01T03:01:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/116","categories":["DataBase"]},{"title":"简单的ajax请求加php逻辑处理","date":"2018-05-31T03:19:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>处理逻辑    html请求页面——&gt;php1——&gt;php2——html显示</p>\n<h3 id=\"php1\">php1<a href=\"post/113#php1\"></a></h3>","link":"post/113","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"php Incorrect Table Name错误","date":"2018-05-29T03:12:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>1.可能是写sql语句的时候，可能是tablename写的多写个空格。<br></p>","link":"post/112","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"php的if和java的if比较","date":"2018-05-21T02:45:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>php中的<code>if</code>语句是<strong>弱类型</strong>，即<code>if（）</code>中的判断语句不必是<strong>boolean类型</strong>的。<br></p>","link":"post/108","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"oracle中 =: 和 :=","date":"2018-05-16T02:50:00.000Z","excerpt":"<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">=: 后面是要接变量</span><br><span class=\"line\">:= 是在存储过程中中接常量值</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","link":"post/74","tags":["procdure","变量","常量值","绑定","赋值"],"categories":["DataBase"]},{"title":"MYSQL中LIMIT用法","date":"2018-05-16T02:42:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>LIMIT是MySQL内置函数，其作用是用于限制查询结果的条数。<br></p>","link":"post/73","tags":["int","limit","pagesize","select","参数","指定","索引"],"categories":["DataBase"]},{"title":"Linux查找含有某字符串的所有文件","date":"2018-05-15T22:17:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>如果你想在当前目录下 查找”hello,world!”字符串,可以这样:<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -rn &quot;hello,world!&quot; *</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/72","tags":["files","grep","pattern","pattern2","匹配","参数","命令","文件","目录"],"categories":["DataBase"]}]}